Package: apihelpers
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions for Making an R Client for an API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mahmoud", "Ahmed",
  email = "mahmoud.s.fahmy@students.kasralainy.edu.eg",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provide functions for constructing a URL, sending requests and
  capturing API responses. The query parameters are checked and formatted
  according to a 'query_map' which describes the type of requests and queries
  allowed by the API.
